I honestly don't want to get rid of twisting. Hey, that keeps the bard player base low. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     But I don't think any other class casts as often as a bard, also, no other class is as unique as a bard. We manage to sing 4 songs at once, while strafing backwards, combining a leather tunic, taking a bite from our veggies and still outrun most mobs.<br>
<br>
But, we cannot sing perfectly, of course not, we're just minor mortals, taking the fight to the homes of the gods, and way beyond, but still, we're not perfect musicians.<br>
<br>
At times like this I realise why we're not famous. Well, apart from the fact that everyone forgets about us every time we get in trouble and fade away from the collective memory. :-) We just can't sing worth ****. I almost feel like we all belong in 'Pop Idol'<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Silly 'I really miss that note sometimes' Sill <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=silinai>Silinai</A> at: 5/10/04 5:20 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall.showUserPublicProfile?gid=brewall>Brewall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Minstrel</span><br>  Posts: 105<br> <font color=#330000>(5/11/04 9:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=19312.topic&index=52>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Fizzle doesn't really affect casters</span><hr size=1> Fizzles between bards and other caster must take into account ALL of the following:<br>
<br>
*Bards cast every tick.<br>
*Bards do not get channeling<br>
*Bards cannot specialize<br>
*MOST IMPORTANTLY: every other class can set up a hotkey that casts twice in row.  Bards cannot do this because the second cast will stop the song if it was successful the first time.<br>
<br>
Net result of the fizzling? Casters may see a couple fizzles in an evening, but simply set up 2xCast hotkeys and forget about it.  Bards see hundreds of missed notes over the course of an evening, pay 45AA's and see barely any reduction, and have to constantly watch the song spam.<br>
